    "title": "Ustraa is Hiring: E-commerce Executive (Junior)",
    "description": "Grow your career with Ustraa! We are hiring a E-commerce Executive for our Coimbatore team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Ustraa:\nUstraa is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Manage email marketing campaigns and push notifications\n• Optimize product pages for search visibility and conversion\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Build and maintain affiliate and influencer marketing programs\n• Collaborate with logistics partners to ensure timely delivery\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Shopify\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Digital Marketing\n• Proficiency in A/B Testing\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n• Proficiency in Facebook Ads\n• Proficiency in Customer Segmentation\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Learning & development budget\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Referral bonus program\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Ustraa!",
